    <p>Beach Road record­ing stu­dio The Base­ment Stu­dio is hold­ing its first live-stream show, to keep alive a scene fraught by the lack of live gigs.</p>
    <p>Fans of met­al­core and hard-core, take note, as home-grown bands Terrestrea (above), Seav­i­sion and Al­le­giance will be per­form­ing. WHEN: To­day, from 8.30pm WHERE: www.face­book.com/ the­base­mentstu­dio.sg</p>

